title: Ring of Fire - January 11 2014
description:
January 11, 2014
Ring of Fire 
Hosted by Robert F. Kennedy Jr., Mike Papantonio and Sam Seder


This week on Ring of Fire Radio:  Representative Keith Ellison will join us to discuss the cutting of unemployment benefits.

Author and journalist Joe Conason will tell us why Republicans are so terrified of Pope Francis.

BillMoyers.com senior digital producer Joshua Holland will explain how gridlock in Washington helps the wealthy elite.

Attorney James Kauffman will discuss the JP Morgan settlement that gets them off the hook for some very serious criminal behavior with Bernie Madoff.
